<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Conjecture" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Conjecture,</orth> subst. 1) guess: H4B Ind. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.198" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 198</bibl> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.3.23" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.1.41" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 1, 41</bibl> <cit><quote>('tis likely, by all --s).</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.250" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 250</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) suspicion: <cit><quote>on my eyelids shall c. hang,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.107" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 107</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as gross as ever touched c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.176" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 176</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>strew dangerous --s in ill-breeding minds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 5, 15</bibl></cit>.
<lb />2) idea, notion: <cit><quote>in my simple --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 30</bibl></cit> (Evans' speech). <cit><quote>now entertain c. of a time,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>